xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: 1. Pick some grain and take it to a windmill to make flour.
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 1. 穀物を摘んで風車でそれを小麦粉にします。
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: generalUI source: skillGuide wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: 2. Use a pot to collect the flour you have made.
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 2. 土鍋に小麦粉を入れます。
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: generalUI source: skillGuide wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: 3. Fill a bucket or jug with water from a sink or fountain.
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 3. シンクか噴水でバケツか水差しに水を入れます。
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: generalUI source: skillGuide wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: 4. Mix the flour and water to make some bread dough.
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 4. 小麦粉に水を混ぜてパン生地を作ります。
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:note: category: interface sub_category: generalUI source: skillGuide wiki_url: None

xliff:trans-unit.xliff:source: 5. Cook the dough by using it with a stove.
xliff:trans-unit.xliff:target: 5. パン生地をストーブで焼きます。
